of lemon.

194
00:09:28,192 --> 00:09:30,778
Unfortunately, there are certain
stars who won’t do what we want.

195
00:09:30,861 --> 00:09:33,406
What’s <i>their </i>problem?

196
00:09:33,489 --> 00:09:34,699
They’re still alive.

197
00:09:34,782 --> 00:09:36,117
And then we thought,

198
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,618
"Who’s good at killing
celebrities?"

199
00:09:39,036 --> 00:09:39,954
Me!

200
00:09:40,037 --> 00:09:41,289
That’s right.

201
00:09:41,372 --> 00:09:43,624
Homer, would you be willing
to acquire some more, um...

202
00:09:43,708 --> 00:09:45,668
uh, accounts for us?

203
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:50,047
Well, you know,
it is awfully hot today.

204
00:09:50,131 --> 00:09:51,549
(chuckles)

205
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,679
Now I’m too cold.

206
