241
00:11:33,526 --> 00:11:34,777
(chuckles)

242
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:36,696
Yes, uh, an outrage.

243
00:11:36,779 --> 00:11:38,698
(clamoring)

244
00:11:38,781 --> 00:11:40,491
(horse whinnying)

245
