about it?

247
00:11:47,081 --> 00:11:48,749
-(clamoring)
-Now wait

248
00:11:48,833 --> 00:11:51,168
just a gosh-darn minute here.

249
00:11:51,252 --> 00:11:54,171
We can’t go taking the law
into our own hands.

250
00:11:54,255 --> 00:11:57,591
