and dreams and-and, uh...

251
00:11:57,675 --> 00:11:59,343
Put a sock in it,
mushmouth!

252
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:00,678
(cheering)

253
00:12:05,182 --> 00:12:06,684
All we are saying is

254
